<p>Postcards and thank-you cards can be used to generate interest  in  the   program. Postcards and thank-you cards are designed to pique interest in the pathway program.  Effective ways   to use postcards and thank-you cards  include:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Share them on Facebook: </strong>These cards are easy to post on social media sites like Facebook. The image could be accompanied by a comment like: "I found a new path to college!" or "I'm going to college at BYU-Idaho Online."</li>
<li><strong>Use them to congratulate and encourage</strong>: Everyone likes getting cards. A good old fashion thank you card can go a long way toward acknowledging others and making them feel important.</li>
<li><strong>Hang 'em up:</strong> Postcards fit nicely in an office window, classroom, and other locations.   <strong><br /></strong></li>
</ul>
<h3>How to get them</h3>
